  "parentId": "c-mo3o0euk-054bbde3ae5f",
  "conclusion": "Patron Anima sits at both pre-decision (interviewed by the Distiller during the pre-plan stage via the ask-patron tool, per c-mo3tvxcv) and post-decision (verdict/override/fill-in on analyst plan decisions, per the c-mo3o28hb output shape). The pre-plan Socratic interview framing (c-mo3phvuw) was dropped after being reshaped into the Distiller. Mid-plan analyst-initiated consultation (c-mo3phwj6) deferred to post-MVP and reparented under the post-MVP bucket.",
